# ===========================================
# KEEP THESE FOLDERS FOR DEPLOYMENT:
# ===========================================
# staticfiles/          - Collected static files (NEEDED for Arvan Cloud)
# static/               - Source static files (NEEDED for collectstatic)
# templates/            - Django templates (NEEDED)
# main/                 - Django app (NEEDED)
# shahin_auto/          - Django project settings (NEEDED)
# requirements.txt      - Python dependencies (NEEDED)
# manage.py             - Django management script (NEEDED)
# Dockerfile            - Docker configuration (NEEDED)
# docker-compose.yml    - Docker compose (NEEDED)
# nginx.conf            - Nginx configuration (NEEDED)
# ===========================================